assertion_line: 63
expression: "get_subcommand_help(\"session\")"
---
List, inspect, and locate session directories

Usage: session <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list  List sessions (20 most recent by default)
  dir   Print the session directory path (for shell composition)
  show  Show detailed info for a session
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
